Oh. man. there's gotta be snacks in here.

828
00:48:25.070 --> 00:48:26.330
Oh. my God.

829
00:48:26.330 --> 00:48:27.450
- Oh. God.
- Santiago!

830
00:48:27.450 --> 00:48:28.700
Oh. God.

831
00:48:28.700 --> 00:48:30.410
Dang!

832
00:48:31.410 --> 00:48:33.000
That's where that guy went!

833
00:48:33.000 --> 00:48:34.920
Oh. my God. What is out there?

834
00:48:45.930 --> 00:48:47.890
- We gotta go now!
- Okay. Go. go. go.

835
00:48:47.890 --> 00:48:49.810
- Let's get out of here.
- Let's go. let's go.

836
00:48:49.810 --> 00:48:51.980
