- Damn it!

840
00:48:54.810 --> 00:48:56.560
- It's a camper van. probably!
- Oh. God!

841
00:48:56.560 --> 00:48:58.770
It's got a split--
a split-charge battery.

842
00:48:58.780 --> 00:49:01.240
The relay probably popped off.
It's underneath the hood.

843
00:49:01.240 --> 00:49:02.650
Kenny. can you fix it?

844
00:49:02.650 --> 00:49:05.030
Usually I could fix it. yes.
but I'm having--

845
00:49:05.030 --> 00:49:08.240
I'm still having some visual problems
because of the...

846
00:49:08.240 --> 00:49:09.740
You did it to me again.

847
00:49:09.740 --> 00:49:14.460
You did it on the wedding video
and now you're wasted off your ass again.

848
00:49:14.460 --> 00:49:15.960
I'm really sorry. boss.

849
00:49:15.960 --> 00:49:19.750
Buffalo sober.
You're Buffalo sober.

850
00:49:19.750 --> 00:49:20.840
Do you have any more?

851
00:49:20.840 --> 00:49:23.050
Griff. please can you fix it?

852
00:49:23.050 --> 00:49:25.050
I think I'm better suited
to be our wheel man.

853
00:49:25.050 --> 00:49:27.180
What are you talking about?
I've always been a better driver than you.

854
00:49:27.180 --> 00:49:28.220
No. you've been a safer driver.

855
00:49:28.220 --> 00:49:30.390
I passed the driver's test
on my first try.

856
00:49:30.390 --> 00:49:31.810
You took three times.

857
00:49:31.810 --> 00:49:33.310
Yeah. but that was 'cause of yield.

858
00:49:33.310 --> 00:49:35.100
I didn't know-- Now I know what that is.

859
00:49:35.100 --> 00:49:37.400
Oh. my God. We're gonna die.

860
00:49:39.570 --> 00:49:40.610
Sorry.

861
00:49:42.400 --> 00:49:43.400
I'll just fix it.

862
00:51:00.060 --> 00:51:01.520
- Doug!
- Go. go. go!

863
00:51:02.320 --> 00:51:03.900
