865
00:51:09.910 --> 00:51:11.070
Oh. shit!

866
00:51:13.830 --> 00:51:15.040
You saw it. right?

867
00:51:15.040 --> 00:51:16.790
What was that? They're not
supposed to get that big.

868
00:51:16.790 --> 00:51:19.620
Oh. God. It was like a dinosaur.

869
00:51:24.000 --> 00:51:25.000
Hey!

870
00:51:27.840 --> 00:51:29.720
